even if you're not keen on it.

147
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:42,879
An absent father is one who is not at home

148
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:44,879
to spend time with his children.

149
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:48,079
And some fathers are disciplinarians.

150
00:05:48,079 --> 00:05:50,959
They have strict rules and they give out punishments.

151
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:53,600
But these days, more fathers are hands-on,

152
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,560
which means that they're very much involved in looking after

153
